# React SPA

- **Canonical:** `apps/template/react-spa` or `apps/<slug>/react-spa`.
- **Layers:** routes `src/routes/`, API `src/api/`, state `src/states/`, types `src/types/`, i18n `src/locales/`, query keys `src/constants/queryKeys.ts`, helpers `src/helpers/`.
- **UI:** prefer `@yca-software/design-system` (workspace `link:../../../packages/design-system` in template). Tailwind content includes `packages/design-system` paths — keep in sync when changing layout.
- **Validate:** `pnpm lint`, `pnpm test`, `pnpm build` in the SPA package directory.
